---

{% from "components/italia-codice-fiscale-input/macro.njk" import italiaCodiceFiscaleInput %}
{% from "components/label/macro.njk" import label %}
{% from "components/field/macro.njk" import field %}

<h2>Default</h2>
{% call field() %}
  {{ label({ for: "italia-codice-fiscale-input-demo", text: "Italian Fiscal Code" }) }}
  {{ italiaCodiceFiscaleInput({ id: "italia-codice-fiscale-input-demo" }) }}
{% endcall %}

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>16 alphanumeric characters: 3 from the surname, 3 from the given name, 5 encoding date of birth and sex, 4 encoding place of birth, and 1 check character.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Italian_fiscal_code">Italian Fiscal Code</a>.</p>
